      "author": "1ordinateur",
      "description": "# Cluddle Callouts 0.1.1\n\nRelease update for submission hardening and publication readiness.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- Keeps the searchable callout picker for built-in and CSS-defined custom callouts.\n- Documents and isolates the read-only config-dir access used to discover enabled CSS snippets.\n- Keeps picker layout styling static in CSS rather than applying layout styling from JavaScript.\n- Ships release assets in GitHub releases rather than tracking `main.js` in the repository.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Desktop only.\n- No network access, accounts, payments, ads, or telemetry.\n- Release assets for this version are `manifest.json`, `main.js`, and `styles.css`.\n",
